al, diplomatic, and commercial networking.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aDiplomatsxTravel. 0aDiplomatszChina. 0aTravel, Medieval. 0aVoyages and travels. 7aHISTORY / Asia / General.2bisacsh  a13th century.  aasian travel.  abaghdad.  abeijing.  achina.  achinese monk.  acommercial networking.  adiplomacy.  adiscussion books.  aengaging.  aeurope.  afirsthand perspective.  aglobal travels.  ahistorical.  ahistory.  aholy land.  aislamic control.  ajerusalem.  alast crusades.  amedieval period.  amongol capital.  amongol empire.  amuslims.  anestorian christian.  anonfiction account.  apilgrimage.  arabban sauma.  atrans eurasian travel.  atravelogue.  awestern travel.  awestern world.  aworld history.  axanadu.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052026237940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094613240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520946132423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520946132/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY